  "lyrics": "\ud83c\udfb5 \ud83c\udfb5Everyday I hear the radio\ud83c\udfb5 \ud83c\udfb5Telling me to go past the line\ud83c\udfb5 \ud83c\udfb5I know you're not a nighting\ud83c\udfb5 \ud83c\udfb5I know it's right\ud83c\udfb5 \ud83c\udfb5Feel the winds in every way\ud83c\udfb5 \ud83c\udfb5In the race in overpay\ud83c\udfb5 \ud83c\udfb5Got money spending dollars on a day\ud83c\udfb5 \ud83c\udfb5Do you know it's just a vacay?\ud83c\udfb5 \ud83c\udfb5I don't know but you want that so\ud83c\udfb5 \ud83c\udfb5Now I know and you feel it all\ud83c\udfb5 \ud83c\udfb5You feel it all\ud83c\udfb5 \ud83c\udfb5Lost in the times that keep changing\ud83c\udfb5 \ud83c\udfb5Want this to make it more than it seems\ud83c\udfb5 \ud83c\udfb5To be in the dark\ud83c\udfb5 \ud83c\udfb5You know I'm just like, baby can you feel it?\ud83c\udfb5 \ud83c\udfb5Can you feel it?\ud83c\udfb5 \ud83c\udfb5The moment that it's real\ud83c\udfb5 \ud83c\udfb5Is it really you?\ud83c\udfb5 \ud83c\udfb5Curtain dropped over mine\ud83c\udfb5 \ud83c\udfb5Curtain dropped over time\ud83c\udfb5 \ud83c\udfb5Curtain black was all we kept\ud83c\udfb5 \ud83c\udfb5The sound of lying that you hear\ud83c\udfb5 \ud83c\udfb5It's just a sign that you fear\ud83c\udfb5 \ud83c\udfb5It's just the, the only thing that makes you here\ud83c\udfb5 \ud83c\udfb5When silence, through everything that left you\ud83c\udfb5 \ud83c\udfb5Lost everything that is dear to you\ud83c\udfb5 \ud83c\udfb5Love\ud83c\udfb5 \ud83c\udfb5Die, die\ud83c\udfb5 \ud83c\udfb5Love, love, love\ud83c\udfb5 \ud83c\udfb5Times that made me all upset\ud83c\udfb5 \ud83c\udfb5And every single laugh\ud83c\udfb5 \ud83c\udfb5You triggered with your embers\ud83c\udfb5 \ud83c\udfb5The embers of my righteous daughter\ud83c\udfb5 \ud83c\udfb5It's my disaster\ud83c\udfb5 \ud83c\udfb5How can you take away my last hour?\ud83c\udfb5 \ud83c\udfb5It's my disaster\ud83c\udfb5 \ud83c\udfb5How do you make it?\ud83c\udfb5 \ud83c\udfb5Nothing but vaguelines\ud83c\udfb5 \ud83c\udfb5That we crossed\ud83c\udfb5 \ud83c\udfb5It just was the moment that we lost\ud83c\udfb5 \ud83c\udfb5Your hand\ud83c\udfb5 \ud83c\udfb5Your face\ud83c\udfb5 \ud83c\udfb5I need the best for each day\ud83c\udfb5 \ud83c\udfb5Invested in seed\ud83c\udfb5 \ud83c\udfb5I was just fetal, just complicated\ud83c\udfb5 \ud83c\udfb5Repeated\ud83c\udfb5 \ud83c\udfb5Hated\ud83c\udfb5 \ud83c\udfb5Denied\ud83c\udfb5 \ud83c\udfb5Exasperated\ud83c\udfb5 \ud83c\udfb5Nuclear war\ud83c\udfb5 \ud83c\udfb5Nuclear war\ud83c\udfb5 \ud83c\udfb5Anything in the galaxy\ud83c\udfb5 \ud83c\udfb5I might think I need to get my cranium checked\ud83c\udfb5",
  "lyricsSegments": [
    {
      "end": 9.020000457763672,
      "text": "\ud83c\udfb5",
      "start": 8.0600004196167
    },
    {
      "end": 16.559999465942383,
      "text": "\ud83c\udfb5Everyday I hear the radio\ud83c\udfb5",
      "start": 14.300000190734863
    },
    {
      "end": 20.139999389648438,
      "text": "\ud83c\udfb5Telling me to go past the line\ud83c\udfb5",
      "start": 17.219999313354492
    },
    {
      "end": 24.399999618530273,
      "text": "\ud83c\udfb5I know you're not a nighting\ud83c\udfb5",
      "start": 20.920000076293945
    },
    {
      "end": 27.459999084472656,
      "text": "\ud83c\udfb5I know it's right\ud83c\udfb5",
      "start": 24.399999618530273
    },
    {
      "end": 31.459999084472656,
      "text": "\ud83c\udfb5Feel the winds in every way\ud83c\udfb5",
      "start": 28.18000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 34.7400016784668,
      "text": "\ud83c\udfb5In the race in overpay\ud83c\udfb5",
      "start": 31.459999084472656
    },
    {
      "end": 38,
      "text": "\ud83c\udfb5Got money spending dollars on a day\ud83c\udfb5",
      "start": 34.7400016784668
    },
    {
      "end": 41.18000030517578,
      "text": "\ud83c\udfb5Do you know it's just a vacay?\ud83c\udfb5",
      "start": 38
    },
    {
      "end": 45.41999816894531,
      "text": "\ud83c\udfb5I don't know but you want that so\ud83c\udfb5",
      "start": 41.18000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 49.880001068115234,
      "text": "\ud83c\udfb5Now I know and you feel it all\ud83c\udfb5",
      "start": 45.41999816894531
    },
    {
      "end": 53.540000915527344,
      "text": "\ud83c\udfb5You feel it all\ud83c\udfb5",
      "start": 49.880001068115234
    },
    {
      "end": 58.18000030517578,
      "text": "\ud83c\udfb5Lost in the times that keep changing\ud83c\udfb5",
      "start": 54.900001525878906
    },
    {
      "end": 63.720001220703125,
      "text": "\ud83c\udfb5Want this to make it more than it seems\ud83c\udfb5",
      "start": 59.08000183105469
    },
    {
      "end": 67.31999969482422,
      "text": "\ud83c\udfb5To be in the dark\ud83c\udfb5",
      "start": 64.44000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 71.12000274658203,
      "text": "\ud83c\udfb5You know I'm just like, baby can you feel it?\ud83c\udfb5",
      "start": 67.31999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 71.80000305175781,
      "text": "\ud83c\udfb5Can you feel it?\ud83c\udfb5",
      "start": 71.12000274658203
    },
    {
      "end": 73.68000030517578,
      "text": "\ud83c\udfb5The moment that it's real\ud83c\udfb5",
      "start": 71.80000305175781
    },
    {
      "end": 74.95999908447266,
      "text": "\ud83c\udfb5Is it really you?\ud83c\udfb5",
      "start": 73.68000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 76.86000061035156,
      "text": "\ud83c\udfb5Curtain dropped over mine\ud83c\udfb5",
      "start": 74.95999908447266
    },
    {
      "end": 78.31999969482422,
      "text": "\ud83c\udfb5Curtain dropped over time\ud83c\udfb5",
      "start": 76.86000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 80.87999725341797,
      "text": "\ud83c\udfb5Curtain black was all we kept\ud83c\udfb5",
      "start": 78.31999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 84.45999908447266,
      "text": "\ud83c\udfb5The sound of lying that you hear\ud83c\udfb5",
      "start": 80.87999725341797
    },
    {
      "end": 87.9000015258789,
      "text": "\ud83c\udfb5It's just a sign that you fear\ud83c\udfb5",
      "start": 84.45999908447266
    },
    {
      "end": 93.55999755859375,
      "text": "\ud83c\udfb5It's just the, the only thing that makes you here\ud83c\udfb5",
      "start": 87.9000015258789
    },
    {
      "end": 98.58000183105469,
      "text": "\ud83c\udfb5When silence, through everything that left you\ud83c\udfb5",
      "start": 93.55999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 103.76000213623047,
      "text": "\ud83c\udfb5Lost everything that is dear to you\ud83c\udfb5",
      "start": 98.58000183105469
    },
    {
      "end": 106.13999938964844,
      "text": "\ud83c\udfb5Love\ud83c\udfb5",
      "start": 105.0999984741211
    },
    {
      "end": 110.58000183105469,
      "text": "\ud83c\udfb5Die, die\ud83c\udfb5",
      "start": 108.5
    },
    {
      "end": 122.80000305175781,
      "text": "\ud83c\udfb5Love, love, love\ud83c\udfb5",
      "start": 110.58000183105469
    },
    {
      "end": 126.55999755859375,
      "text": "\ud83c\udfb5Times that made me all upset\ud83c\udfb5",
      "start": 123.37999725341797
    },
    {
      "end": 129.55999755859375,
      "text": "\ud83c\udfb5And every single laugh\ud83c\udfb5",
      "start": 126.55999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 132.3000030517578,
      "text": "\ud83c\udfb5You triggered with your embers\ud83c\udfb5",
      "start": 129.55999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 136.89999389648438,
      "text": "\ud83c\udfb5The embers of my righteous daughter\ud83c\udfb5",
      "start": 132.3000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 139.33999633789062,
      "text": "\ud83c\udfb5It's my disaster\ud83c\udfb5",
      "start": 136.89999389648438
    },
    {
      "end": 143.9600067138672,
      "text": "\ud83c\udfb5How can you take away my last hour?\ud83c\udfb5",
      "start": 139.33999633789062
    },
    {
      "end": 146.82000732421875,
      "text": "\ud83c\udfb5It's my disaster\ud83c\udfb5",
      "start": 143.9600067138672
    },
    {
      "end": 149,
      "text": "\ud83c\udfb5How do you make it?\ud83c\udfb5",
      "start": 146.82000732421875
    },
    {
      "end": 151.75999450683594,
      "text": "\ud83c\udfb5Nothing but vaguelines\ud83c\udfb5",
      "start": 149
    },
    {
      "end": 152.86000061035156,
      "text": "\ud83c\udfb5That we crossed\ud83c\udfb5",
      "start": 151.75999450683594
    },
    {
      "end": 157.25999450683594,
      "text": "\ud83c\udfb5It just was the moment that we lost\ud83c\udfb5",
      "start": 152.86000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 160.5399932861328,
      "text": "\ud83c\udfb5Your hand\ud83c\udfb5",
      "start": 158.5399932861328
    },
    {
      "end": 163.67999267578125,
      "text": "\ud83c\udfb5Your face\ud83c\udfb5",
      "start": 161.67999267578125
    },
    {
      "end": 166,
      "text": "\ud83c\udfb5I need the best for each day\ud83c\udfb5",
      "start": 163.67999267578125
    },
    {
      "end": 167.63999938964844,
      "text": "\ud83c\udfb5Invested in seed\ud83c\udfb5",
      "start": 166
    },
    {
      "end": 170,
      "text": "\ud83c\udfb5I was just fetal, just complicated\ud83c\udfb5",
      "start": 167.63999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 173.77999877929688,
      "text": "\ud83c\udfb5Repeated\ud83c\udfb5",
      "start": 172.86000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 175.05999755859375,
      "text": "\ud83c\udfb5Hated\ud83c\udfb5",
      "start": 174.13999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 175.24000549316406,
      "text": "\ud83c\udfb5Denied\ud83c\udfb5",
      "start": 175.05999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 177.24000549316406,
      "text": "\ud83c\udfb5Exasperated\ud83c\udfb5",
      "start": 176.32000732421875
    },
    {
      "end": 180.66000366210938,
      "text": "\ud83c\udfb5Nuclear war\ud83c\udfb5",
      "start": 178.82000732421875
    },
    {
      "end": 184.05999755859375,
      "text": "\ud83c\udfb5Nuclear war\ud83c\udfb5",
      "start": 182.22000122070312
    },
    {
      "end": 186.9199981689453,
      "text": "\ud83c\udfb5Anything in the galaxy\ud83c\udfb5",
      "start": 184.27999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 192.94000244140625,
      "text": "\ud83c\udfb5I might think I need to get my cranium checked\ud83c\udfb5",
      "start": 186.9199981689453
    }
